This job ({{ job_name }}) is intended to exercize
a very minimal localhost-only runthrough of ADEPT.
It should exercize the basic job-system and check
critical variable-handling, then exit.  It's intended
to be run by the test_exekutir_xn.sh unittest script
as well as an automated ADEPT-ci job for testing
code-changes.

